title: Week 15 Buy or Sell + Playoff Prep, Dynasty Download - Fantasy Football Podcast for 12/15
description:
The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode heading into Week 15! On today’s fantasy football podcast, get ready for the fantasy playoffs with a handful of questions answered, injury updates, and a new edition of Buy or Sell! Plus, a preview of the Thursday Night matchup between the Chiefs and Chargers, and a Dynasty Download! Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast -- Fantasy Football Podcast for December 15th, 2021.
  
 (06:10) - Buy or Sell
 (14:20) - News & Notes
 (23:45) - Thursday Night Breakdown - Chiefs at Chargers
 (32:15) -  Dynasty Download
 (41:35) - Mailbag
 (41:55) - Noah Fant or Pat Freiermuth this week?
 (42:55) - Lock non-playoff teams?
 (48:20) - Ezekiel Elliott or Javonte Williams?
 (52:10) - Miles Sanders, Jordan Howard, Boston Scott
